These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-1::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, azalea, daisy, orchid
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, january, november, september, april
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who growsdaisy##7
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
4. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
6. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsazalea##7
7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaisy##5
8. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |        2        |      3       |     4      |      5      |
| Flower           | daisy | azalea | orchid | poppy | rose    |
| Birthday   | january      | march          | april   | september     | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-2::.
5 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, poker, chess, billiard
The people have 5 different jobs:  mechanic, fisherman, pilot, teacher, chef
1. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
2. the person playing billiard is between the person playing bridge and the teacher##2
3. the teacher is on the right of the pilot##1
4. the chef is on the far right##1
5. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
6. the mechanic is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person playing billiard is somewhere between the person playing chess and the fisherman##7
8. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |   3    |     4     |   5   |
| Game        | backgammon | bridge | billiard | poker | chess  |
| Job   | mechanic   | fisherman   | pilot | teacher     | chef |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-3::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: funk, rock, soul, r&b, d&b
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, cola, almond-milk, soy-milk
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the fan funk##1
2. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
3. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking almond-milk##7
4. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
5. the fan funk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan r&b##3
7. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the fan d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Music-Genre          | soul  | d&b   | r&b | rock      | funk |
| Beverage   | sprite | cola | water   | almond-milk | soy-milk  |

