.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-4::.
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, dog, fish, guinea-pig, hamster
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, mirinda, fanta, almond-milk
1. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
2. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |    5     |
| Pet   | goldfish | guinea-pig | fish | hamster    | dog |
| Beverage     | almond-milk     | fanta     | mirinda | cola | tea     |

