2. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
6. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
7. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person playing billiard and the person eating zucchini##7
8. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Game   | snooker | billiard | canasta | scrabble | backgammon |
| Food           | papaya    | carrot | artichoke    | eggplant    | zucchini    |

