.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-6::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving, hiking, chess, fishing
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, golf, cycling, badminton
1. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
2. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
3. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
9. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |    3    |     4     |      5       |
| Hobby   | fishing | puzzles | hiking  | chess | skydiving |
| Sport           | volleyball    | water-polo  | golf | cycling    | badminton        |

