.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-7::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, car, skateboard, trike
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, october, august, march, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the car##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
11. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |   2   |       3       |      4      |   5    |
| Transport   | skateboard | trike | motorbike | jet-ski | car  |
| Birthday        | october     | september   | august          | march    | may |

