.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-8::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea, daffodil, orchid, aconite
City: miami, london, berlin, prague, rome
1. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
2. the person traveling to miami is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere between the person who growsaconite and the person traveling to rome##7
5. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person traveling to london is not the person who growsbellflower##6
7. the person who growsbellflower is the person traveling to rome##1
8. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1
9. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |    3     |  4  |   5    |
| Flower   | daffodil    | bellflower | azalea | aconite | orchid |
| City        | london | rome      | berlin    | miami | prague    |

