4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
5. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the security-guard is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking almond-milk##7
8. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
9. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the musician##5

.:: Answer ::.
