.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-10::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, scooter, van, roller
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, coral, amber, ebony, turquise
 1. the person who likes light-blue is the person who likes light-blue##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person who likes turquise##6
 3. the person who likes ebony is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes light-blue is the person driving the bike##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person who likes amber is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person driving the scooter##7
 9. the person who likes coral is not the person driving the scooter##6
10. the person driving the roller is the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Transport   | roller | snowmobile | van | scooter     | bike       |
| Color      | ebony   | coral    | amber | turquise | light-blue |

